1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 15=
(A Circus of Wolves)

3
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,560
Mu Shaoze?

4
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,560
Mr. He.

5
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,640
This is my wife's room.

6
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,519
It is late.

7
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,519
What's up?

8
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:43,959
You are still here.

9
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,159
I should be asking you that.

10
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,840
Mr. He, you came so late with wine.

11
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:52,560
Are you here to drink with Madam Gu?

12
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,560
Sorry, we are busy.

13
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,400
What do you mean?

14
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,599
Exactly what I said.

15
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,840
We are still busy.

16
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:01,239
We don't want to be disturbed.

17
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:03,439
Go away.

18
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,159
This is my wife's room.

19
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,799
He Jinchen.

20
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:08,759
What are you doing?

21
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,639
We are discussing
next week's marketing plan.

22
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,000
He is helping me review the data.

23
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,080
Discussing a plan?

24
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,840
Does he have to stay so late?

25
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,360
You know I'm recovering, right?

26
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,800
All of today's work

27
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,120
was done in this room.

28
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:25,360
If you have nothing urgent, go rest.

29
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:26,360
For that wine,

30
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,919
keep it for yourself.

31
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,479
I...

32
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,840
Did you do that on purpose?

33
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,680
Let's continue.

34
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,719
Meiyan International's
use of prohibited raw materials

35
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,080
is just too well hidden.

36
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,319
With the evidence we have now,

37
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:57,360
it is not enough to destroy them.

38
00:02:58,759 --> 00:02:59,439
You're right.

39
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,080
The victims we contacted before

40
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,240
were either silenced

41
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,400
or too afraid to come forward
due to lack of evidence.

42
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,599
The chemical ingredients

43
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,360
cause irreversible damage to the skin.

44
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,719
She's barely in her twenties,

45
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,280
and her face is completely ruined.

46
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:17,879
What can we do

47
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:21,240
to get those victims to step forward?

48
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,159
I have an idea.

49
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:29,159
We can launch
a charitable recovery program

50
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,439
under the resort's name.

51
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:34,719
We can recruit women

52
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,400
whose skin has been damaged

53
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,080
because of using substandard cosmetics.

54
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,639
We can provide them

55
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:42,319
with free recovery
and skin repair treatments.

56
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:43,240
First,

57
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,319
it is a charity event.

58
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,560
It will build a great reputation
for the resort.

59
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,319
It's better than any marketing plan.

60
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,439
Second...

61
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,120
Second,

62
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,719
these victims are direct evidence.

63
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,360
Their stories

64
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:56,000
and the condition of their skin

65
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:59,319
are irrefutable proof
against Meiyan International.

66
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,599
Exactly.

67
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,599
During the recovery process,

68
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:05,520
we can collect their testimonies
and relevant evidence.

69
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,439
Then,

70
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,919
these witnesses will be our trump card.

71
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:11,599
I'll reach out to

72
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,319
a professional dermatology team tomorrow

73
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:16,079
and have them put together a proposal.

74
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,160
Alright.

75
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,879
Get some rest.

76
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,399
Take care of your injury.

77
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,319
I will send you the proposal tomorrow.

78
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:25,680
No problem.

79
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,000
Lock the door.

80
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,399
There is a hungry wolf next door.

81
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,600
Don't worry.

82
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,160
He won't get into my room easily.

83
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,160
Then...

84
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,720
I'm leaving now.

85
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,519
Good night.

86
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,120
Good night.

87
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,439
Hello.

88
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,160
Send a big gift to He Jinchen tomorrow.

89
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,040
It is time

90
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,439
to watch them tear each other apart.

91
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,800
That animal!

92
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,079
Boss,

93
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,600
as you requested,

94
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,720
we found out

95
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:34,120
Gu Qingmei once sold
many pieces of jewelry

96
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,519
and gave all the money to He Jinchuan

97
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,600
for investments and to pay off debts.

98
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:43,340
(Product images)

99
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:46,959
These are all Gu Qingmei's
jewelry pieces.

100
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,800
Didn't I just give her these two?

101
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,240
These two pieces

102
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:57,160
were just sold by He Jinchuan.

103
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,040
He Jinchuan!

104
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:02,759
How dare you touch my woman!

105
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,839
Don't blame me for
forgetting our brotherhood.

106
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:10,720
He Jinchuan!

107
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,399
You dare to block me?

108
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,680
Are you trying to ditch me?

109
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:15,680
Baby,

110
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:19,040
I just signed a probation agreement
with Xu Niannian.

111
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,399
Once I get through this period,

112
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:22,160
the Xu family fortune will all be mine.

113
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,360
Don't be mad.

114
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,759
Let me sing you a song.

115
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:30,199
Love you for ten thousand years.

116
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,460
(Dear)

117
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,560
What do I do?

118
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,399
Pick it up!

119
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,399
Dear, where are you?

120
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,199
I'm working late at the office today.

121
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,439
I will be home late.

122
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,639
You must be so tired.

123
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:56,120
You... don't stay up too late.

124
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:56,720
Alright.

125
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:04,000
Baby, you are so smart.

126
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,800
He Jinchuan!

127
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,600
Dear!

128
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,519
So this is what you call working late?

129
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,040
Working late on a woman?

130
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,360
Dear, let me explain!

131
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,920
Didn't you say that besides Xu Niannian,

132
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,920
your legal wife,

133
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,040
I'm the only woman?

134
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,959
Who do you think you are to hit me?

135
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:49,759
Trash!

136
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:50,720
- Try this!
- Beat him!

137
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,399
You played with my feelings!

138
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,000
Stop it! Stop it!

139
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,199
You played with my feelings!

140
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,000
Dear, I was wrong! Dear!

141
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,800
You trash!

142
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,639
Stop it!

143
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,040
Stop it!

144
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,079
What a piece of trash!

145
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,439
Help! Dear!

146
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,000
Stop it!

147
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:06,600
Thanks.

148
00:08:06,759 --> 00:08:07,560
I'll kill you!

149
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,439
Stop! Stop!

150
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:10,839
Disgusting!

151
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,240
Dear!

152
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:14,959
Beat him!

153
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:18,199
Nothing beats watching him
get torn down.

154
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:20,720
So tell me,

155
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,920
if we just make him
walk away with nothing,

156
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,399
is it too easy for him?

157
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:25,639
Don't worry.

158
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:27,040
For someone like him,

159
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,839
how could he pass up
such a perfect opportunity

160
00:08:28,959 --> 00:08:30,680
to eliminate his rival?

161
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,759
You're right.

162
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,960
I have always had one question.

163
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,519
Why did you set the trap for He Jinchuan

164
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:42,080
so early?

165
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,559
Because he was also present

166
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,879
at the fire eight years ago.

167
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,879
They did it together?

168
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,480
I found out

169
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:59,399
that He Jinchuan was interning
at the Meiyan factory back then.

170
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:02,159
He was also having an affair
with He Jinchen's secretary.

171
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,639
They were in the office that day.

172
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,120
So He Jinchuan was a witness?

173
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,519
More or less.

174
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,320
His secretary said

175
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,960
they hid behind the sofa that day

176
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,759
and overheard

177
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,120
He Jinchen arguing with my father

178
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,480
about the raw materials.

179
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,720
He Jinchuan wanted to hold leverage
over his brother,

180
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,720
so he recorded it in secret.

181
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,559
Therefore,

182
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,639
you want to turn the brothers
against each other completely,

183
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,240
so you can get the recording
from He Jinchuan.

184
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,039
Xu Niannian has been a big help.

185
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,279
That's true.

186
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:43,639
(Divorce Agreement)

187
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,399
(Divorce Agreement)
Let us get a divorce.

188
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,679
This is the last time.

189
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:46,840
Please forgive me one more time.

190
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,240
Niannian, I can't live without you!

191
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:48,879
Niannian!

192
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:51,039
You can't live without me?

193
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:53,399
I swear

194
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,440
everything I said is true.

195
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,600
Alright then.

196
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,440
Finish this,

197
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:02,480
and I will give you one more time.

198
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,720
Dear,

199
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,080
what... what is this?

200
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:10,720
It is the supplement
you carefully prepared for me.

201
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:12,480
Come on, finish it.

202
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,799
(One bowl of it)

203
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,240
(will not kill me.)

204
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,320
Oh, I forgot to tell you.

205
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,120
All the supplements in the study room

206
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,960
are in this bowl.

207
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:35,919
What is going on?

208
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,440
Dad.

209
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:41,120
I have been married to
He Jinchuan for years,

210
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:42,960
and he has been keeping
a string of women outside.

211
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,279
He even poisoned me.

212
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,879
I want a divorce.

213
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:46,639
What?

214
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,120
Poison?

215
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,200
You are lying!

216
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,600
You are the one who poisoned me!

217
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,679
You tried to kill me!

218
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:55,440
Only rock sugar and bird's nest in it.

219
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:57,399
You are just feeling guilty.

220
00:10:58,399 --> 00:11:00,759
Why don't we go to the study room,
grab your medicine bottles,

221
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:01,799
and get them tested right now?

222
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:09,399
Dad.

223
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,799
These are all evidence.

224
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,879
Either he signs now,

225
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,679
or I call the police.

226
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,080
Adultery plus intentional harm,

227
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:24,879
he could spend a few years in prison.

228
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,159
You animal!

229
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,919
You have disgraced our family!

230
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:33,639
You...

231
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,559
Jinchen!

232
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:36,639
You are finally home!

233
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,000
Please talk to them for me!

234
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,799
They won't forgive me!

235
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,000
Dad.

236
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,480
Today, I found out

237
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:46,360
that Jinchuan

238
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,120
embezzled fifty million from the company

239
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,080
and has not repaid it.

240
00:11:54,039 --> 00:11:56,320
I was just about to ask you
how to handle it.

241
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,820
(Loan Agreement)

242
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,440
After all,

243
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,679
he is family.

244
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,399
You...

245
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,399
You animal!

246
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,399
I'm still alive!

247
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:12,679
You treat Shengda
as if it is already yours!

248
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,919
Starting today,

249
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:16,000
you are stripped of all positions.

250
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,440
All your shares will be taken back.

251
00:12:17,759 --> 00:12:18,240
Dad!

252
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,039
Useless!

253
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:21,120
No need.

254
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:22,679
According to our agreement,

255
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:25,559
all assets under his name
now belong to me.

256
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:33,480
Niannian,

257
00:12:34,159 --> 00:12:35,080
at this point,

258
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,600
I agree to the divorce.

259
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:39,919
But...

260
00:12:41,159 --> 00:12:41,840
Don't worry.

261
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,440
We will not treat you unfairly.

262
00:12:46,639 --> 00:12:47,440
Thank you, Dad.

263
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,120
You animal!

264
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:02,960
He Jinchen!

265
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,159
You are my brother!

266
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,600
And you kicked me when I was down!

267
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:17,240
Now you remember I'm your brother?

268
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:19,120
What did you do to your sister-in-law?

269
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:25,879
You want to be my rival?

270
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,440
You are not worthy.

271
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:43,919
Niannian!

272
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:44,600
Niannian!

273
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:45,480
Niannian!

274
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:47,759
Niannian, don't be mad!

275
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,360
Niannian!

276
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,080
Niannian, listen to me!

277
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,159
Niannian!

278
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,000
Niannian, even if you leave me,

279
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,159
you cannot leave our child!

280
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,360
You are a mother!

281
00:13:55,759 --> 00:13:56,799
You cannot abandon your own child!

282
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:57,440
Niannian!

283
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:59,159
I've sent An'an to the Xu family.

284
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,960
After the divorce, he will live with me.

285
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,600
Niannian!

286
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:02,960
An'an cannot grow up without a father!

287
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:03,840
He is still young!

288
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,440
We need to give him a complete family!

289
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,080
Niannian!

290
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,840
Don't guilt-trip me with our child!

291
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,480
A father like you

292
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,480
will only lead him down the wrong path.

293
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,159
Niannian!

294
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:11,960
Niannian, let me explain!

295
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,559
Niannian!

296
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:13,519
He Jinchuan!

297
00:14:14,639 --> 00:14:15,679
Do you really think I'm that stupid?

298
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,159
When I loved you,

299
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,000
I could be dumb.

300
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:21,799
But don't insult my intelligence.

301
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,600
So you knew all along.

302
00:14:27,159 --> 00:14:28,399
You have been playing along with me.

303
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,679
From the moment you tricked me
into signing that agreement,

304
00:14:31,759 --> 00:14:32,600
to catching me at the club,

305
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:33,559
to forcing me into divorce,

306
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,879
it was all your scheme, step by step,

307
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,360
to strip me of everything.

308
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,519
You brought it all on yourself.

309
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:45,840
You are so ruthless, Xu Niannian!

310
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,759
I treated you so well,

311
00:14:47,879 --> 00:14:48,519
tried so hard to please you,

312
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:49,559
and this is how you repay me!

313
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,000
You again, imposter!

314
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,960
You encouraged Niannian
to get a divorce!

315
00:14:58,759 --> 00:14:59,000
He Jinchuan!

316
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,039
I will never let you go!

317
00:15:00,159 --> 00:15:00,879
He Jinchuan!

318
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:02,480
Even now

319
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,240
you still think this is not your fault?

320
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,840
You deserve to end up alone

321
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,879
and left with nothing.

322
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:08,799
Let's go.

323
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,399
You...

324
00:15:35,380 --> 00:15:40,140
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

325
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:44,980
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

326
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:49,540
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

327
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:54,460
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

328
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:58,260
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

329
00:15:58,260 --> 00:16:03,060
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

330
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:05,900
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

331
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:08,580
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

332
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:14,500
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

333
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:21,700
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

334
00:16:21,980 --> 00:16:26,660
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

335
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:33,620
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

336
00:16:33,940 --> 00:16:40,740
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

337
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:45,420
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

338
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:48,780
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

339
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:55,700
♪Right as I confess my love♪
